About all in one food app , that helps in restaurant discovery and food social media , that helps the restaurant pull genuine crowd , - not for offers or discount as in other table reservation apps
Helping restaurants to save alot of money that they spend on table reservation apps, 
first the restaurant has to pay an annual subscription and then commission per table and then on compulsory discounts .
Our idea just requires the restaurant to pay 3x of the annual subscription , out of which we use 2x  as packets of money given to customers as offers to spend it back to the restaurant , 
so here the restaurant at the end of the year has only paid 1x of annual subscription and in  return has got a genuine fanbase.
we also have expanded the scope into emerging as a food social media app by provinding a chat section , meal planner section , and a posts and reels section .
Cutomer can see the entire restaurant ,every nuke  and corner beforehand, like a google earth vision , and can order before hand , the food items and book a table. 
The restaurants can now just pay for the annual subscription(3x the subscription of other table reservation apps ) without commision per table and save alot of money ,
we use the annual subscriptions as packets of money given to customers as offers that go back to the restaurant itself . 
